{"tid":1726373,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我on9到喊到暈左 入左醫院","createTime":"2019-11-16T06:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T15:09:22.000Z","uid":205770,"like":23,"dislike":217,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0f8d1842e9591a786f13b0f7eb1ca26e26a916","tid":1726373,"uid":205770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"有咩方法可以令自己平靜 因為呢排香港咁 我前幾日出去行街 仆到腳損哂 聞到tg 已經好唔舒服.琴日因為感情問題 學業問題 又係到mon post 見到香港變到咁樣.自己屈住 頂唔順 一邊食飯 一邊喊 之後暈低左 我屋企人放工先發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌<br />\n好撚唔開心 全部野都好灰<br />\n同個男仔曖昧1年無結果 我斬纜唔搵佢 佢最近呢幾日搵返我 唔知佢想點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我之前斬因為個男仔出左好幾次post <br />\n我仲可以點算 佢搵返我 我心軟keep contact 突然琴日又人間蒸發咁 無消息 頂 我係咪做左水泡啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係醫院一起身 就諗起佢 好心煩 好攰<br />\n明明旅行又去過 家長又見過 行街都佢同我行  拖左1年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢主動時我縮 避開哂佢signal 佢係咪因為我唔主動 心淡先用交友app 我係咪做錯左啊 好後悔 好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢揾返我做乜撚 傾幾日又唔傾幾日 <br />\n個個收我放手 叫我醒 我仲覺得佢主動搵我有一絲希望呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2個月前 隔離post有巴幫我占 話我同佢之後會有contact<br />\n叫我唔可以鐘意佢 佢心態係死仆街 想我主動追佢 想搵我就揾 唔想就放我一邊 會做左水泡<br />\n琴日入左院我朋友睇唔過眼 又係識占卜 話我心態已經崩潰左 佢話個男對我有意思 不過有太多顧慮同壓力 我同佢要溝通 溝通就會開花結果 有希望<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2個講野完全唔同 我都係半信半疑 我想講我真係唔知on9到幾迷信先去占卜 又太感情用事 喊到入院 感情好煩 學業好煩 原本諗住之後同朋友行街 岩岩出院 又行唔到 醫生叫我留屋企 好好休息 咁我就係咁亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌 鐘意一個人好煩 怪自己on9 佢咁廢 我都咁鐘意佢<br />\n<br />\n打完心情好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你地聽我發洩<br />\n最後想講<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n我下星期先再出 今星期唔得了 身心疲累 隻腳跑果陣仲仆到跛下跛下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98e92673da99f90e0b4e8912f4d3d30e0480b24","tid":1726373,"uid":181581,"like":47,"dislike":7,"score":40,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:36:13.000Z","msg":"正<br />\n新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2716b7bde662a3beba38177bd5bb8022ee77a5be","tid":1726373,"uid":22974,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:37:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3ecf11bf57dfd1ee728ea3f24ffb8c7a37173f4","tid":1726373,"uid":205770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e98e92673da99f90e0b4e8912f4d3d30e0480b24","tid":1726373,"uid":181581,"like":47,"dislike":7,"score":40,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:36:13.000Z","msg":"正<br />\n新潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:37:43.000Z","msg":"有咩咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f57ae87ae00092b4f32e2b26333cc08a405f18","tid":1726373,"uid":205770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2716b7bde662a3beba38177bd5bb8022ee77a5be","tid":1726373,"uid":22974,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:37:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:38:16.000Z","msg":"你當我係啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65804e5f75f6ba16df0104648ae297450eebe255","tid":1726373,"uid":249885,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"咪嘈啦 以前日本仔打香港我都係咁捱啦 你班友要生要死 真係唔捱得"},{"pid":"e2c1c83c3b0aa499ffc31893a1eb9ba44329affa","tid":1726373,"uid":210165,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:41:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af58eb5c34cc553d328ce2d40a0d9761b0d664a1","tid":1726373,"uid":308961,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:41:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38122049701dbc0411ee341d5b79a48379cd6deb","tid":1